EN: Vaccines are one of the effective ways to prevent infectious diseases.

ZH: 我们要重视环境保护，防止自然灾害的发生。
EN: We should pay attention to environmental protection to prevent natural disasters.

ZH: 防止干燥的唇部产生裂口，可以经常使用润唇膏。
EN: Applying lip balm regularly can prevent dry and cracked lips.
